node.text:
🔴 | Jadon Sancho... HERE WE GO!

After 16 months negotiations, @sanchooo10 joins @manchesterunited on a permanent deal from Borussia Dortmund. 🤝

- “The chance to join Manchester United is a dream come true and I just cannot wait to perform in the Premier League. This is an exciting squad”. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

- Final fee €85m plus agents fee. Contract until June 2026 signed in the last days with option to extend the deal until June 2027. 🚨

How do you rate this deal? HERE WE GO 👇🏻🔴

#sancho #manchesterunited #manunited #utd #jadonsancho #mufc #united #herewego 🌟

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fabrizio Romano in Tottenham Hotspur Stadium with @guardian, @harrykane, @transfers, @433, @transfermarkt_official, and @cbssportsgolazo. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
⚪️ | Harry Kane’s future situation

There’s still no agreement reached now between Manchester City and Tottenham for Harry Kane 🚨

- Tottenham are denying rumours about Harry Kane set to join Manchester City, same from City side. ⚠️

- Daniel Levy wants to keep Kane at the club and the same from Fabio Paratici, there’s nothing agreed between clubs. 🤝

- Manchester City are interested and they consider Harry Kane their main target together with Jack Grealish but NO fee agreed with Spurs. 🔴

- Last bid from Manchester City was one month ago: £100m and players available, turned down by David Levy few days later. ❌

- Harry Kane will talk with Tottenham board and Nuno to discuss about his future soon. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

#thfc #tottenham #spurs #manchestercity #mcfc #city #kane #harrykane #herewego #transfers

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fabrizio Romano in Tottenham Hotspur Stadium with @guardian, @transfers, @433, @transfermarkt_official, and @cbssportsgolazo. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
⚪️ | Tottenham-Sevilla swap deal!

EXCL. Tottenham and Sevilla are now finalizing a new swap deal... then here we go soon! 🤝

- Erik Lamela to Sevilla, Bryan Gil to Tottenham: the agreement is set to be completed on a permanent deal for both players. 🔃

- Sevilla will also receive €25m from Spurs and there will be add ons included in the negotiation. 🇪🇸

What do you think about this swap deal? 👀👇🏻

#sevilla #tottenham #lamela #bryangil #spurs #transfers #sevillafc #thfc #herewego 🇪🇸🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fabrizio Romano in Old Trafford with @guardian, @transfers, @433, @transfermarkt_official, and @cbssportsgolazo. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'VARANE'.

node.text:
🔴 | Varane’s position on his future

New updates for @raphaelvarane future with Manchester United pushing to sign him 🇫🇷

- Raphaël Varane and his agents confirmed to Real Madrid his desire to try a new experience in the Premier League. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

- Varane will be respectful waiting for the club agreement between Manchester United and Real Madrid, still not completed - but he wants Man United as next challenge. 🔴

- Varane will be respectful with Real Madrid and will NEVER break with the club also if he’s out of contract in 10 months. He’s gonna wait for the to clubs to complete the deal, once the official bid will be on the table soon. 🤝

- Real Madrid were trying again to change his mind... but together with his representatives, Varane also confirmed to Manchester United that he’d be ‘ready’ to accept their contract bid until June 2026 if the agreement will be completed with Real Madrid. Personal terms have never been a problem. ⏳

#realmadrid #varane #mufc #manchester #epl #manchesterunited #real #transfers #herewego

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fabrizio Romano in Tottenham Hotspur Stadium with @transfers, @piergollo, @433, @transfermarkt_official, @guardian_sport, and @cbssportsgolazo. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
⚪️ | Gollini > Tottenham, here we go!

@piergollo is now set to join Tottenham as new goalkeeper from Atalanta in the next days 🇮🇹

- First deal of new Spurs director of football Fabio Paratici will be the Italian goalkeeper coming from Atalanta, considered a “perfect deal for present and future” by Tottenham board. 🧤

- The agreement is set to be completed on loan until June 2022 + option to extend the loan until Junr 2023 + buy option for Spurs. 🤝

- Buy option price for Tottenham will be €15m, could become an obligation to buy in case some targets [caps and more] will be achieved during the loan spell with Spurs. 💰

- Gollini has reached an agreement on personal terms with Tottenham and the deal is now at final stages with contracts to be signed. ⏳

- He’s been in the Italian National team for many years and considered one of the best GK in Serie A. He’s been already playing in England at Manchester United academy and Aston Villa. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

- Cristian Romero is also on the list among centre back targets for Tottenham, but there’s still no total agreement w/Atalanta for the Argentinian CB. 🇦🇷

#gollini #pierluigigollini #tottenham #spurs #epl #thfc #italy #football #transfers #herewego 🇮🇹

node.text:
🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿 | Ben White deal, here we go!

@ben_white6 will join Arsenal on a permanent deal, agreement now confirmed and here we go 🤝

- Arsenal have completed the agreement to sign Ben White, £50m guaranteed fee to Brighton. Contract until June 2026. ⚪️🔴

- Medicals will be completed once White will come back from holidays after Euro2020. The deal is done and first paperworks have been signed. ⏳

- Ben White only wanted to join Arsenal since first contacts started weeks ago. Everton never made an official bid for Ben White. 🌟

- Arsenal are planning to announce Sambi Lokonga in the next few days after total agreement reached with Anderlecht, then Ben White once medicals are completed. Both deals are DONE. ✍🏻

- Manuel Locatelli deal is still complicated as Italy midfielder priority is joining Juventus. Arsenal are ready to match Sassuolo price tag for Locatelli offering €40m but Juventus are frontrunners, as he wants to join Juve. There’s still no agreement between Juventus and Sassuolo, as of today. 🇮🇹

#arsenal #afc #benwhite #white #lokonga #epl #transfers #arsenalfc #brighton #herewego 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fabrizio Romano in Estadio Santiago Bernabéu with @guardian, @transfers, @433, @raphaelvarane, @transfermarkt_official, and @cbssportsgolazo. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
🔴 | Raphaël Varane deal update

It’s time for final decision for @raphaelvarane on his future in the next days, work in progress! 🇫🇷

- After direct talks re started 4 days ago, now Manchester United are preparing an official bid to Real Madrid for Raphaël Varane. 🚨

- Varane has not answered yet to Real Madrid contract extension proposal and his current agreement expires in June 2022. ⚪️

- Manchester United made a contract proposal to Varane until June 2026 and consider personal terms ‘not an issue’ on this deal since days. 📑

- Varane wants a Premier League experience and he’d accept Man Utd proposal if/when Real and Manchester United boards will reach an agreement. He’ll be respectful with Real as they’ve to decide on his transfer now. 🤝

- Florentino Perez is waiting for Varane to come back from his holidays then they’ll decide about next steps with Real Madrid involved. ⏳

#realmadrid #varane #mufc #manchester #epl #manchesterunited #real #transfers #herewego

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fabrizio Romano in Camp Nou (FC Barcelona) with @guardian, @transfers, @433, @transfermarkt_official, and @cbssportsgolazo. May be an image of 2 people and people playing sports.

node.text:
🚨 | Griezmann-Saúl deal updates

Barcelona and Atletico are in advanced talks for the swap deal between Saúl and Griezmann! 🇪🇸

- Both players gave the green light in the last hours on a potential move to Barça and Atléti. 🔄

- The two clubs are now negotiating on price tags for Griezmann and Saúl. Barça want money included in the negotiation and both could be permanent. 🗣

- Liverpool and Chelsea are keen on Saúl if swap deal with Barcelona will collapse in the next days, but Saúl priority is Barça. 🔴

#saul #griezmann #barcelona #atleti #fcb #barça #transfers #atleticomadrid #herewego

node.text:
🔵🔴 | No doubt: Messi will STAY

@leomessi never had any doubt: as reported in the past weeks, he’s 100% staying at Barcelona 🇦🇷

- The agreement has been reached since weeks and is set to be announced in the next days. ⏳

- Messi had an agreement on a new deal with Barcelona until June 2023, but he’s gonna sign a five-years contract to help the club with his salary paid on long term, as per @esportsrac1. 🤝

- Messi’s new contract will be until June 2026 and there will be a clause included for €600m. 📑

- Now it’s just a matter of time for the official announcement from Barça and Messi team. ✍🏻

Never been in doubt: Messi stays, here we go! 🐐

#messi #leomessi #barcelona #fcb #barça 🌟 #transfers #lionelmessi #football #herewego

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fabrizio Romano in Estadio Santiago Bernabéu with @guardian, @transfers, @433, @raphaelvarane, @transfermarkt_official, and @cbssportsgolazo. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
🇫🇷 | Raphaël Varane future updates

Manchester United are pushing to sign Varane this summer as new centre back main target 🔴

- Manchester United are now back in direct contact with Real Madrid for Raphaël Varane, after talks opened weeks ago to ask about the CB. 🚨

- Red Devils board confirmed the intention to sign Varane as main target, official bid to be made once they’ll know Real final position and price tag. 🗣

- As of now there’s still NO official price or official position from Real Madrid. They’re waiting for Varane to come back from holidays. ⚪️

- Negotiations on personal terms are considered ‘not an issue’ by Manchester United board. 🤝

- Varane is out of contract in June 2022 with Real Madrid, Ancelotti will try to chance he wants to try something different after many years. 🌟

- Jules Koundé, Pau Torres, Cristian Romero are among the options considered by Man United as centre backs but Varane is the priority right now, if Real Madrid will let him leave. 🔴

#realmadrid #varane #mufc #manchester #epl #manchesterunited #real #transfers #herewego

node.text:
🚨 | Sancho completed his medical

@sanchooo10 has completed today his medical as new @manchesterunited player! 🔴🤝

- Manchester United and Borussia Dortmund have signed all paperworks of Jadon Sancho deal, after agreement in principle announced days ago. 📑

- Sancho signs with Man Utd until June 2026 with option to extend the agreement until 2027. €85m guaranteed to B. Dortmund + agents fee. 🔴

- Manchester United are now preparing the ‘real’ official announcement with Sancho wearing the new kit for the season 2021/2022. 👕📸

Sancho > Man United, here we go confirmed 🏁🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

#sancho #manchesterunited #manunited #utd #jadonsancho #mufc #united #herewego 🌟

node.text:
5.02 AM. Milano, Italy. 💙🇮🇹

Impossible to explicate how proud we are of this team, group, family. These guys are incredible.
